{"tid":1847493,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"應承我，如果今次因為政府把關不力而導致武肺社區爆發，我哋嘅訴求將會升級為香港獨立","createTime":"2020-01-28T05:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T04:12:04.000Z","uid":253978,"like":97,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b56703c6bab147fc15b6a3a1d31b84aa21e6c727","tid":1847493,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"3abc4eab10824d2deec23bbe9951cbffe5b61a53","tid":1847493,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:35:08.000Z","msg":"一早要獨"},{"pid":"40a4f3ed28e4a113c0090228c532c7235a3a4f6e","tid":1847493,"uid":253978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"cf6eb08a974b0957654c5080b2476ea008f89fa3","tid":1847493,"uid":168169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"0246209f3b508e9ffab1baf627d196a732a8c94a","tid":1847493,"uid":59297,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"大家依排成日屌嘅封關、港人優先，全部都要香港獨立先會實現到"},{"pid":"b23ee29132c1834c28ce1da32c446330f7d6f67c","tid":1847493,"uid":229920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:39:59.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"a287be87f6e91a9913fe2a193aa854dd07e2c0aa","tid":1847493,"uid":342354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b609723dbb77548bd35558ebe32bf65fb5db7c83","tid":1847493,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[事關重大請廣傳]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人<br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aMf1RYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaMf1RYs.jpg&h=d189414d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLMVDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLMVDM.jpg&h=058fd92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服<br />\n「要死一起死」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7qtpw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7qtpw7.jpg&h=11a8b2cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66a408d0b8ee9b6e4ab6fe7b2a1e223eb24f09da","tid":1847493,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0246209f3b508e9ffab1baf627d196a732a8c94a","tid":1847493,"uid":59297,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"大家依排成日屌嘅封關、港人優先，全部都要香港獨立先會實現到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"咁少人like<br />\n睇黎大家都唔想獨立"},{"pid":"dab9ccda94cd98709aa8a093d6ea3ef7f9e8f000","tid":1847493,"uid":11703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"訴求同要求獨立本身已經係予盾<br />\n你點求中國畀你獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3ab87beced6065c46b4f017e8dd686d0eabd56","tid":1847493,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T05:48:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b676ccdeec01a180d38d9ce816ca0a42ca3b76f2","tid":1847493,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dab9ccda94cd98709aa8a093d6ea3ef7f9e8f000","tid":1847493,"uid":11703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01